    "body": "Hey guys ðŸ‘‹ \r\n\r\nMany 3rd party plugins make use of custom highlight groups and signs for the left column. For highlight groups there is this neat feature with the `default` parameter. This simply allows plugin developers to add highlight groups with sane defaults, but the user can easily customize them. This can happen before the plugin gets loaded or afterwards. The plugin must not provide any logic or setup function to support this. It just works out of the box.\r\nIt would be amazing if the same mechanism could work for `sign define`. It makes the customization of plugins stupid simple for the user without headache for plugin developers.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to habe productive discussions regarding this feature request. Thanks!",
